    <div class="container legal-content">
        <h1>Terms of Service</h1>

        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-8">Last updated: June 4, 2025</p>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-light mb-4 text-gray-900">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            By accessing or using AnswerLayer's AI-powered data analytics platform (the "Service"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service ("Terms"). If you disagree with any part of these terms, you may not access the Service.
