          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-light mb-4 text-gray-900">2. Description of Service</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            AnswerLayer provides an AI-powered data analytics platform that enables users to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
            <li>Query databases using natural language</li>
            <li>Connect to various data sources (PostgreSQL, BigQuery, AWS Athena, etc.)</li>
            <li>Generate automated visualizations and insights</li>
            <li>Create dashboards and reports</li>
            <li>Manage data connections and security settings</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mb-4">
            Our Service uses artificial intelligence and machine learning to translate natural language queries into database commands and provide intelligent data analysis.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-light mb-4 text-gray-900">3. User Accounts and Registration</h2>
