          <p class="mb-4">
            If any provision of these Terms is found to be unenforceable, the remaining provisions will remain in full force and effect.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-light mb-4 text-gray-900">16. Contact Information</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            For questions about these Terms, please contact us:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
            <li>Email: legal@getanswerlayer.com</li>
            <li>Support: josh@getanswerlayer.com</li>
            <li>Website: https://www.getanswerlayer.com</li>
