        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-light mb-4 text-gray-900">17. Entire Agreement</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            These Terms, together with our Privacy Policy and any additional terms for specific features, constitute the entire agreement between you and AnswerLayer regarding the Service.
          </p>
